QuestData.Title: Call of Air - Jeztor's Fleet
QuestData.CompletionText: You've worked hard, $n, but we have only just begun!$b$bMy War Riders must taste in the flesh of their targets. This will ensure a surgical strike against our enemies!$b$bMy fleet is the second most powerful in our air command. Thusly, they will strike at the more powerful of our adversaries. For this, then, they need the flesh of the Stormpike Lieutenants.$b$bMake haste, soldier!
QuestData.RewardText: More! More! Bring more for they are soon to be ready!
